{"tid":1046560,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"異性朋友原來係要保持返一定距離","createTime":"2019-03-04T10:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T13:45:04.000Z","uid":71253,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"eb7c44a63fc64df1243e881894bc73ca4a2c26e2","tid":1046560,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T10:52:39.000Z","msg":"細個以為男女都係咁<br />\n岩傾就可以做朋友，做兄弟<br />\n但大個左發現原來如果我對個個兄弟冇興趣個陣，而佢想同我做熟既朋友，原來我係會好反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會想每堂都同佢一齊上，唔會想每次落堂都一齊去溫書，唔會想日日一齊食飯，唔會想佢太關心自己，唔會想接受佢既幫忙<br />\n<br />\n而家真係信成為密友總帶著愛<br />\n<br />\n唔係鍾意佢根本就唔想比佢知自己咁多野<br />\n<br />\n定係得我係咁？<br />\n<br />\n利申：絲打讀緊和尚科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"226e86a542fd956344dc329907d8dcfd60000480","tid":1046560,"uid":226216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T10:54:17.000Z","msg":"遲早冇朋友"},{"pid":"12807fd14bd9de9d9c170f40aafde2b24f0cd28a","tid":1046560,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T10:55:40.000Z","msg":"你都on9<br />\n要交月費架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b98e51ee21d4d8a48263126f69b6da5e61729f","tid":1046560,"uid":192571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T10:56:45.000Z","msg":"似想食左妳多d"},{"pid":"82d1faa7dc1cfc82fb6f89af2f2e855e7be259be","tid":1046560,"uid":71253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"226e86a542fd956344dc329907d8dcfd60000480","tid":1046560,"uid":226216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T10:54:17.000Z","msg":"遲早冇朋友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T10:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明白左呢個道理就會盡量同異性同學保持距離<br />\n淨係做同學/普通朋友<br />\n希望唔會嚇走人"},{"pid":"64d2859cc6d2b682926f69e0415b4c8c3bf635b3","tid":1046560,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27b98e51ee21d4d8a48263126f69b6da5e61729f","tid":1046560,